<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    Deputies Sign Statement Rejecting Foreign Intervention </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   PA2505041894 Mexico City XEW Television Network in Spanish 
0430 GMT 24 May 94 </F>

<F P=103> PA2505041894 </F>
<F P=104>  Mexico City XEW Television Network </F>
<F P=105>  Spanish </F>


<TEXT>
BFN 

<F P=106> [From the "24 Hours" newscast] </F>
  [Excerpt] [passage omitted] During today's [23 May] 
session, all the political parties represented in the Chamber of 
Deputies signed a political statement regarding foreign 
observers for the upcoming elections. Felipe Munoz, a deputy 
for the Institutional Revolutionary Party, read the document. 
  [Begin Munoz recording] In light of recent statements by 
U.S. 
