<F P=103> PA2505195094 </F>
<F P=104>  Panama City Circuito RPC Television </F>
<F P=105>  Spanish </F>


<TEXT>
BFN 

<F P=106> [Statement by Boris Moreno, private secretary for Panamanian </F>
President-elect Ernesto Perez Balladares, in Santa Fe de Bogota 
on 23 May; from the "RPC Television News" newscast -- recorded] 
  [Text] President-elect Perez Balladares arrived at Eldorado 
Airport at 0900 today. He was accompanied on his approximately 
six-hour visit by his official delegation, which included future 
Foreign Minister Gabriel Lewis Galindo and presidential adviser 
Jose Luis Sosa. The president-elect was received at Eldorado 
Airport by Colombian Foreign Minister Noemi Sanin de Rubio and 
other officials. 
  The president-elect made a courtesy visit to EL TIEMPO 
