rise in the price of the dollar. In this context, we must 
remember that volatile forces affect the market, and that 
sometimes they cause situations that go beyond reasonable and 
expected limits. The process is being monitored in a very 
responsible and careful manner to ensure that state mechanisms 
[words indistinct] freely and [word indistinct]. [end recording] 
