<TEXT>
BFN 

  [Excerpt] [passage omitted] In a statement made by a 
spokesman for the Foreign Ministry, the Algerian authorities 
urge the parties to the conflict in Yemen to stop bloodshed in 
order to establish domestic peace and stick to dialogue to 
resolve the dispute and preserve the unity of Yemen. The 
statement further says that Algeria affirms its preparedness to 
continue mediation efforts whether at national level or in the 
