  [Text] Tripoli, 1 May -- Brother Umar Mustafa al-Muntasir, 
the secretary of the General People's Committee for Foreign 
Liaison and International Cooperation, has sent a message to 
Hamed Algabid, the secretary-general of the Islamic Conference 
Organization [ICO]. 
  In his letter he calls for the necessary contacts to be made 
regarding the call to ICO member countries to hold an emergency 
session of the conference of ICO foreign ministers before the 
