officers, responsible for this. Let them tell us the truth, 
what is the secret behind this classification? Let us hear the 
plain facts. 
  Now 'Ali Salim al-Bid is contacting the outside world saying 
the 3d Brigade is still fighting and that [words indistinct] its 
hardware and soldiers. Is it like this? Have you not [words 
indistinct] with each other? [crowd shouts "yes"] He contacts 
