Your sons and brothers are afraid. This is true, because they 
are concerned about you as you may be detained, imprisoned, 
[word indistinct], tortured, and measures could be taken against 
them, and, perhaps, they could be liquidated. 
  People [words indistinct] wrong, wrong. In other words, 
[words indistinct]. It happened between colleagues. Enough, 
enough [words indistinct]. This is so because no one would 
benefit from it. However, now everyone [words indistinct] and 
safeguards his colleague. You are brothers and comrades in 
